title: SEC Shorts - Alabama needs an ambulance
author: SEC Shorts
description: Alabama went into Kyle Field as the number one ranked team in the country. They left Kyle Field with their first loss to an unranked opponent in 100 tries.  Now they need expert medical and football care after such a harrowing defeat.
